source(output(
		RowID as long,
		LeadId as string,
		Status as string,
		CampaignId as string,
		CreatedDate as timestamp,
		LeadSource as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	isolationLevel: 'READ_UNCOMMITTED',
	query: 'select * from(\nSELECT ROW_NUMBER()\n               OVER ( PARTITION BY cm.LeadId ORDER BY cm.createdDate asc) AS \'RowID\',\n       cm.LeadId, cm.Status, cm.CampaignId, CreatedDate, LeadSource\nfrom ods.SF_CampaignMember cm\nwhere LeadId is not null\n    ) as x\nwhere RowID = 1\n',
	format: 'query',
	staged: true) ~> OriginalCampaignDataset

FilterLastModified select(mapColumn(
		LeadFirstName = FirstName,
		LeadId = Id,
		LeadLastName = LastName,
		LeadFullName = Name,
		LeadBirthday = Birthdate__c,
		LeadAddress = Street,
		LeadEmail = Email,
		CreatedById,
		LastModifiedById,
		LeadPhone = Phone,
		LeadMobilePhone = MobilePhone,
		NorwoodScale = NorwoodScale__c,
		LudwigScale = LudwigScale__c,
		HairLossInFamily = HairLossFamily__c,
		HairLossProductUsed = HairLossProductUsed__c,
		HairLossSpot = HairLossSpot__c,
		LeadPostalCode = PostalCode,
		City,
		State,
		LeadEthnicity = Ethnicity__c,
		LeadGender = Gender__c,
		LeadLanguage = Language__c,
		LeadStatus = Status,
		CreatedDate,
		LastActivityDate,
		LeadMaritalStatus = MaritalStatus__c,
		LastModifiedDate,
		LeadSource,
		DoNotCall,
		DoNotContact = DoNotContact__c,
		DoNotEmail = DoNotEmail__c,
		DoNotMail = DoNotMail__c,
		DoNotText = DoNotText__c,
		ConvertedContactId,
		ConvertedAccountId,
		ConvertedOpportunityId,
		ConvertedDate,
		DiscStyle = Disc__c,
		LeadExternalId = External_Id__c,
		IsDeleted,
		ServiceTerritoryId = Service_Territory__c,
		GCLID = GCLID__c,
		ReferralCode = Referral_Code__c,
		ReferralCodeExpirationDate = Referral_Code_Expiration_Date__c,
		PromoCode = Promo_Code__c,
		Occupation__c
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> SelectLeadColumns
IsValid, SelectGeography join(lower(iif(length(replace(LeadPostalCode, ' ',''))==6, left(LeadPostalCode, 3), LeadPostalCode)) == lower(DigitZIPCode),
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinGeography
DimGeography select(mapColumn(
		GeographyKey,
		DigitZIPCode
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> SelectGeography
ODSLead filter(LastModifiedDate <= currentTimestamp() && toDate(LastModifiedDate) > toDate(addDays(currentTimestamp(), $DaysToLoad*-1))) ~> FilterLastModified
JoinGeography, SelectDateColumnsCreated join(toDate(CreatedDate) == FullDateCreated,
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinDateCreated
JoinDateActivity, SelectTimeCreated join(second(CreatedDate) == Second
	&& hour(CreatedDate) == Hour
	&& minute(CreatedDate) == Minute,
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinTimeOfDay
DimDate select(mapColumn(
		DateKeyActivity = DateKey,
		FullDateActivity = FullDate
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> SelectDateColumnsActivity
DimTimeOfDay select(mapColumn(
		TimeOfDayKeyCreated = TimeOfDayKey,
		Second,
		Hour = Hour24,
		Minute
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> SelectTimeCreated
JoinPromotion derive(LeadFirstName = iif(regexMatch(LeadFirstName,`[a-zA-Z]+`), initCap(regexReplace(LeadFirstName, `([0-9])|[!@#$%^&*(),.?:;+´~|\[\]{}|<>\/_-]`,'')) ,initCap(regexReplace(LeadFirstName, `[()-]`,''))),
		LeadLastname = iif(regexMatch(LeadLastName,`[a-zA-Z]+`), initCap(regexReplace(LeadLastName, `([0-9])|[!@#$%^&*(),.?:;+´~|\[\]{}|<>\/_-]`,'')) ,initCap(regexReplace(LeadLastName, `[()-]`,''))),
		LeadFullName = iif(regexMatch(LeadFullName,`[a-zA-Z]+`), initCap(regexReplace(LeadFullName, `([0-9])|[!@#$%^&*(),.?:;+´~|\[\]{}|<>\/_-]`,'')) ,initCap(regexReplace(LeadFullName, `[()-]`,''))),
		LeadBirthday = toDate(LeadBirthday),
		LeadPhone = replace(replace(replace(replace(LeadPhone,'(',''),')',''),' ',''),'-',''),
		LeadMobilePhone = replace(replace(replace(replace(LeadMobilePhone,'(',''),')',''),' ',''),'-',''),
		SourceSystem = 'Salesforce',
		GeographyKey = iifNull(GeographyKey,-1),
		EthnicityKey = coalesce(EthnicityKey, -1),
		GenderKey = coalesce(GenderKey, -1),
		LanguageKey = coalesce(LanguageKey, -1),
		StatusKey = coalesce(StatusKey, -1),
		CreatedDateKey = coalesce(DateKeyCreaated, -1),
		CretaedTimeKey = coalesce(TimeOfDayKeyCreated,-1),
		LeadLastActivityDate = LastActivityDate,
		LastActivityDateKey = coalesce(DateKeyActivity,-1),
		LastActivityTimekey = coalesce(TimeOfDayKeyActivity, -1),
		LeadSource = initCap(LeadSource),
		LeadCreatedDate = CreatedDate,
		SourceKey = coalesce(SourceKey, -1),
		MaritulStatusKey = coalesce(MaritalStatusKey, -1),
		DWH_LastUpdateDate = currentTimestamp(),
		DWH_CreatedDate = currentTimestamp(),
		CampaignKey = coalesce(CampaignKey, -1),
		CenterKey = coalesce(CenterKeyDimCenter,-1),
		CenterNumber = CenterNumber,
		Promotionkey = coalesce(Promotionkey, -1)) ~> CalculateFinalsColumns
JoinDateCreated, SelectDateColumnsActivity join(toDate(LastActivityDate) == FullDateActivity,
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinDateActivity
DimTimeOfDay select(mapColumn(
		Hour,
		Minute,
		Second,
		TimeOfDayKeyActivity = TimeOfDayKey
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> SelectTimeActivity
DimDate select(mapColumn(
		DateKeyCreaated = DateKey,
		FullDateCreated = FullDate
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> SelectDateColumnsCreated
FilterBySourceSystem select(mapColumn(
		EthnicityKey,
		EthnicityName
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> SelectEthnicityColumns
FilterBySourceSystemGender select(mapColumn(
		GenderKey,
		GenderName
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> SelectGenderColumns
DimLanguage select(mapColumn(
		LanguageKey,
		LanguageName
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> SelectLanguageColumns
FilterByGroupAndSource select(mapColumn(
		StatusKey,
		StatusName
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> SelectStatusColumn
DimStatus filter(lower(SourceSystem) == 'salesforce' && lower(StatusGroup) == 'lead') ~> FilterByGroupAndSource
DimMaritalStatus select(mapColumn(
		MaritalStatusKey,
		MaritalStatusName
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> SelectMaritalStatusColumn
DimSource select(mapColumn(
		SourceKey,
		SourceName
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> SelectSource
JoinTimeOfDay, SelectEthnicityColumns join(lower(trim(LeadEthnicity)) == lower(trim(EthnicityName)),
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinEthnicity
JoinEthnicity, SelectGenderColumns join(lower(trim(LeadGender)) == lower(trim(GenderName)),
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinGender
JoinGender, SelectLanguageColumns join(trim(lower(LeadLanguage)) == lower(trim(LanguageName)),
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinLanguage
JoinLanguage, SelectStatusColumn join(lower(trim(LeadStatus)) == lower(trim(StatusName)),
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinStatus
JoinStatus, SelectMaritalStatusColumn join(lower(trim(LeadMaritalStatus)) == lower(trim(MaritalStatusName)),
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinMaritalStatus
JoinMaritalStatus, SelectSource join(lower(trim(LeadSource)) == lower(trim(SourceName)),
	joinType:'left',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> JoinSource
